Answer.Comments: In the section at the beginning and in the middle where you are being tested on individual gestures, there is a "right" or "wrong" screen. The graphic on both screens is broken/missing.  Also, when testing the phrases, there were some sentences where "na" would appear, i.e. "was the na kicked by the fireman?" The phrasing was very confusing and lead to me selecting the wrong answer more than once.

Title: Multitasking Memory Test - Learn some gesture symbols and remember sequences.  Test your memory!

Answer.Comments: probably the most exhausting and difficult hit i have done in my 10 months on doing M Turk hits.  very long study.  also i didn't realize until about the 10th set of words that we were supposed to list the words in the same order they were presented; i think that was the case.  also a few times the word "na" appeared which threw me for a loop.  on the bright side, thanks for your generosity and best wishes.
